The paper deals with the recognition of graphic symbols in technical documents, which is a problem in the field of document image analysis. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of a statistical classifier and a Bayesian network for symbol recognition suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
